      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000132",
    "sentence": "吳楚反時，弓高侯功冠諸將。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000133",
    "sentence": "傳子至孫，孫無子，國絕。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000134",
    "sentence": "嬰孫以不敬失侯。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000135",
    "sentence": "穨當孽孫嫣，貴幸，名顯當世。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000136",
    "sentence": "嫣弟說，以校尉擊匈奴，封龍額侯。",
