  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000147",
    "sentence": "子寶嗣，亡子，國除。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000148",
    "sentence": "成帝時，繼功臣後，封增兄子岑為龍額侯。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_033_000149",
